		<text xml:lang="EN"><![CDATA[BuildDouble is a modified version of Scratch 2.0 developped by the MIT Media Lab, with new features interacting with electronic modules in Arduino Eco-system. Scratch is a project of the Lifelong Kindergarten group at the MIT Media Lab. It is available for free at http://scratch.mit.edu]]></text>
	</description>

